Big Bank and DJ Scream discuss stimulus checks, Georgia opening back up and welcome Wiz Khalifa to discuss his new project "The Saga Of Wiz Khalifa." Wiz Khalifa also discusses hit battles, his son Bash, cannabis talk, Michael Jordan vs Lebron and more!
